===============================================================================
HOW TO USE THE EXAMPLES?
===============================================================================

1. Compile Code:
   [a] Fortran90 Compiler 
       (tested: Sun (SUNW,Sun-Blade-1000), OS 5.8 
		/ Compiler: Sun WorkShop Compiler Fortran 90 2.0):

       make -f makefile_f90

   or
   [b] Intel Fortran Compiler
       (tested: Intel XEON CPU 3.0GHz, SuSE Linux 9.0
		/ Compiler: Intel(R) Fortran Compiler 8.0):

       make -f makefile_ifc

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2. Run the code:
   
   [a] execute miex
       (follow instructions in Appendix A "Test Run")

   or
   [b] Example 1:    miex < 1.in
       Example 2:    miex < 2.in

===============================================================================
